342
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:56,720
Leaders, come on.

343
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,480
Everyone,

344
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,720
leaders and experts,

345
00:10:58,799 --> 00:10:59,320
