346
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,559
Come, come.

347
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,440
Over here.

348
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:02,960
Hanxuan's dad.

349
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,440
Hanxuan's father.

350
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,519
Come here, young man.

351
00:11:09,399 --> 00:11:10,120
All right.

352
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:11,879
Thank you.

353
