392
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:04,840
Come on.

393
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:05,639
Thank you.

394
00:12:05,799 --> 00:12:06,519
Thank you.

395
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:07,039
Congratulations.

396
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:07,679
Congratulations.

397
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:10,080
Come on.

398
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:11,399
Have another drink.

399
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,200
Sit, sit.

400
00:12:12,399 --> 00:12:12,720
Thank you.

401
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:13,159
Hanxuan,

402
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,279
