403
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,440
I'm fine.

404
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,279
I'm fine.

405
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:17,240
Come on.

406
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:18,879
Dad.

407
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:21,080
