408
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,879
He just loves drinking.

409
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,720
Don't only eat vegetables.

410
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,039
Have some meat.

411
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:28,440
What, are you drunk?

412
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,080
He's had too much.

413
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,559
What's wrong? Do you feel unwell?

414
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:32,519
He's drunk.

415
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,080
Go lie down.

416
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:36,840
Eldest!

417
00:12:37,559 --> 00:12:38,120
Eldest!

418
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,440
What's wrong with your father?

419
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,440
He's fine, Auntie.

420
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,600
He's always like this.

421
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:42,919
He loves drinking.

422
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:43,600
Dad.

423
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,559
Come on.

424
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,960
Let's go sleep.

425
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,799
Go lie down.

426
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:47,720
Dad.

427
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:49,679
Dad.

428
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,200
Dad!

429
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:52,080
What's wrong?

430
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,279
