434
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:56,879
Sir.

435
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,320
Sir, wake up.

436
00:13:03,799 --> 00:13:04,399
Come help.

437
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:05,480
Move him over there.

438
00:13:07,519 --> 00:13:07,840
Grandpa!

439
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,519
One, two, three.

440
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:10,399
Slowly.

441
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,879
Everyone, move aside.

442
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,279
Spread out.

443
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,519
Keep the air circulating.

444
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,919
Sir. Sir.

445
00:13:16,039 --> 00:13:16,919
He just drank too much.

446
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,279
No pulse or breathing.

447
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,399
Find an AED and call 120.

448
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:20,840
There's one in my car.

449
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,320
I'll help.

450
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,240
I'll call 120.

451
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:23,879
Move those tables and chairs.

452
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,759
Clear a path.

453
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:32,639
Do not touch the patient.

454
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,879
Analyzing heart rhythm.

455
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,440
Shock advised. Charging.

456
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,360
Charging complete. Press the red button.

457
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:45,840
Clear.

458
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:46,679
Shock.

459
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:52,639
Shock delivered.

460
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,080
Dad!

461
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,720
It is now safe to touch the patient.

462
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:58,759
