463
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,080
Sir, wake up.

464
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,399
Can you hear me?

465
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,159
Uncle.

466
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:06,600
Sir.

467
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,080
What's wrong?

468
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:07,639
What happened?

469
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:08,080
What's wrong?

470
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:09,279
What's wrong with you?

471
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:09,799
Stomach pain.

472
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,240
Besides your stomach,

473
00:14:10,279 --> 00:14:11,080
