474
00:14:11,279 --> 00:14:11,679
It hurts.

475
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:12,799
Where else?

476
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:13,600
Dizzy.

477
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:14,840
Hold him upright.

478
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:17,639
What's wrong?

479
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:18,759
Hey.

480
00:14:19,639 --> 00:14:20,039
Hold him.

481
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:20,840
Spit it all out.

482
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,240
Your stomach hurts too?

483
00:14:23,039 --> 00:14:23,360
Son!

484
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,919
Doctor, please look at him.

485
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,759
What's happening?

486
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:26,840
He has a pulse. Check his blood pressure.

487
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,320
Okay.

488
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,440
It's poisoning.

489
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:29,519
Poisoning?

490
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,399
What?

491
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:31,840
The food was poisoned?

492
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,159
The ingredients were fresh.

493
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,399
I cooked them myself.

494
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,799
We all ate the same dishes.

495
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,440
What's going on?

496
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,600
Only the men are vomiting.

497
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,799
The women and children are fine.

498
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:42,879
Could it be the liquor?

499
00:14:44,159 --> 00:14:44,840
They've been poisoned.

500
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:45,799
Poisoned.

501
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,600
Raw aconite root.

502
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,320
Aconitine poisoning.

503
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,399
Aconitine

504
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,320
can cause malignant arrhythmias,

505
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:55,879
cardiogenic shock,

506
00:14:56,039 --> 00:14:57,320
and circulatory and respiratory failure.

507
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,080
Besides the liquor,

508
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,039
