509
00:15:00,159 --> 00:15:00,720
No, only the liquor.

510
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:02,960
Everyone, move!

511
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:03,879
Start CPR and induce vomiting.

512
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,639
Give supportive medication.

513
00:15:04,679 --> 00:15:05,679
Make him vomit.

514
00:15:05,879 --> 00:15:06,799
Quickly.

515
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:09,440
Mark the critical patients.

516
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:09,759
Okay.

517
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,200
Director Zhao,

518
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,200
