523
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:15,799
Okay.

524
00:15:15,799 --> 00:15:16,519
I'll call emergency services.

525
00:15:17,639 --> 00:15:18,320
Everyone, stay calm.

526
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,399
Doctor, please check him.

527
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,759
Anyone not poisoned, move away.

528
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,240
Leave room for the patients.

529
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,159
This way.

530
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,360
Make way.

531
00:15:24,519 --> 00:15:25,279
Emergency center?

532
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,120
There's been

533
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:27,039
