534
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,159
We need ambulances

535
00:15:28,159 --> 00:15:28,720
and additional support.

536
00:15:28,799 --> 00:15:29,360
Three. Go.

537
00:15:30,639 --> 00:15:31,080
Breathe.

538
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:32,480
The critical patients

539
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,039
go directly to Dongli.

540
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:33,919
Understood.

541
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:34,440
Go.

542
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,639
Slowly.

543
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:36,720
This way.

544
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:38,039
Over here.

545
00:15:39,279 --> 00:15:39,720
Director Zhou,

546
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:40,600
