547
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:41,679
The doctors are here.

548
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:42,799
Patients with red bands are critical.

549
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:43,799
Please take them to Dongli Hospital.

550
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,399
There's another one here.

551
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,480
Take him to Dongli too.

552
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,159
This way.

553
00:15:48,279 --> 00:15:48,759
Keep moving.

554
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,039
It's okay.

555
00:15:53,159 --> 00:15:53,559
Hanxuan.

556
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,120
