567
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:16,720
Auntie.

568
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,360
Ma'am.

569
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:19,120
Auntie.

570
00:16:19,279 --> 00:16:19,639
What's wrong with her?

571
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:20,399
Where does she feel unwell?

572
00:16:21,399 --> 00:16:22,159
Did she drink the liquor too?

573
00:16:22,279 --> 00:16:23,159
No.

574
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,320
She never drinks.

575
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:25,320
Right.

576
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:26,679
Stethoscope. Blood pressure cuff.

577
00:16:26,799 --> 00:16:27,919
Okay.

578
00:16:27,919 --> 00:16:29,039
Ma'am, what's your name?

579
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:30,120
Ma Guilan.

580
00:16:30,159 --> 00:16:30,840
Let her answer.

581
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:32,759
Raise your arm.

582
00:16:33,519 --> 00:16:34,000
Lift it.

583
00:16:34,399 --> 00:16:34,639
Yes.

584
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,039
Raise your arm.

585
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:40,080
Here.

586
00:16:43,559 --> 00:16:44,559
Ready to measure.

587
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,000
