592
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:51,679
7.5.

593
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:52,559
It was fine.

594
00:16:54,279 --> 00:16:55,080
140 over 85.

595
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:55,799
Heart rate, 75.

596
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,039
Her heart rate and blood pressure are normal.

597
00:16:57,919 --> 00:16:58,480
Stroke.

598
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,480
